author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
🎟️ To come and see Justin Hawkins Rides Again LIVE across the UK from January 2026, find tickets here: 
https://www.aegpresents.co.uk/event/justin-hawkins-rides-again/
🎟️ For VIP upgrades: https://thejawsofvictory.com/pages/justin-hawkins-rides-again?srsltid=AfmBOorryy6x7BKwj8HeKF7R1Jdtat6hl3fNPuhRJfMpQWxpCC2o1IqT

I'm going on tour in January with the live version of my YouTube show! Some esteemed bands have agreed to meet me on the road at venues in Scotland, England and Wales, so I thought I'd introduce you to some of them here. Today, I'm speaking to Phoebe Little and Jas Scott from SpaceAcre - but you won't find them on Spotify - for reasons they will explain. 

To watch Why We Left uninterrupted: https://youtu.be/Od33R9VpnPM?si=nGwXTE_ABkkoucFH

To hear more from SpaceAcre, head to: https://bandcamp.com/search?q=spaceacre

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

title: A Leaving Message to Spotify
